### Mixin 使用
```less
// styles/mixins.less
// ✅ 常用 mixin
.flex-center() {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.ellipsis() {
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.multi-line-ellipsis(@lines: 2) {
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-line-clamp: @lines;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  overflow: hidden;
}

// ✅ 响应式 mixin
.responsive(@breakpoint; @rules) {
  @media (min-width: @breakpoint) {
    @rules();
  }
}

// 使用
.my-component {
  .flex-center();
  
  .title {
    .ellipsis();
  }
  
  .description {
    .multi-line-ellipsis(3);
  }
}
```

